summary: AN ORDINANCE abolishing the fee for mailing business licenses to branch locations and two change of location fees, each collected by the Director of Licenses and Consumer Affairs; and amending Seattle Municipal Code Sections 5.44.130B, 6.02.170, and 6.82.140C (Ordinances 72630 Section 12; 48022 Section 9; and 84297 Section 13 respectively) therefor.
